snippet.textDisplay: The real reason only Endeavor could have defeated the High End nomu isn't because of how strong he is, but because he's the only one who refused to accept that All Might had no limits. That just because he couldn't defeat him didn't mean there was any point in not trying. And although that lead to decades of unforgivable abuse of his own family, in this particular moment, that stubborness was invaluable. Because every other pro-hero would have convinced themselves that without All Might, there would be no hope of defeating this monstrosity.
